{"parse":{"title":"Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five (TCG)","pageid":318557,"wikitext":{"*":"{{ExpansionPrevNext | prev=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four | next=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Six}}\n{{TCGPromoInfobox\n|setname=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five\n|logo=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five Logo.png<!--Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four logo.png-->\n|symbol=no\n|cards=86 <!--114 variants-->\n|period=August 14, 2024\n}} \n\n'''Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five''' is a series of promotional cards released on August 14, 2024 through [[Play! Pok\u00e9mon|Pok\u00e9mon Organized Play]] events or affiliated products. This set features 86 specifically selected cards from the {{TCG|Scarlet & Violet}} expansion through {{TCG|Temporal Forces}}, including {{TCG|SVE Basic Energies|SVE prints}} of {{TCG|Energy card|Basic Energy cards}}. All cards retained their original set number, but are marked with the Play! Pok\u00e9mon logo. Each Booster pack contains 6 cards. Foil cards in this set have Cosmos Holofoil except for {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon ex}} and {{TCG|ACE SPEC card}}s which retain their regular foil patterns.\n\n==Card list==\n{{Setlist/header|title=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five|bordercol={{fire color}}|tablecol={{psychic color}}|cellcol={{dragon color}}|textcolor=000000|rarity=yes|symbol=no|promo=yes}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolScarlet and Violet.png|x18px|link=Scarlet & Violet (TCG)]] 081/198|G|[[Miraidon ex (Scarlet & Violet 81)|Miraidon]]{{ex}}|Lightning||Double Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolScarlet and Violet.png|x18px|link=Scarlet & Violet (TCG)]] 086/198|G|[[Gardevoir ex (Scarlet & Violet 86)|Gardevoir]]{{ex}}|Psychic||Double Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolScarlet and Violet.png|x18px|link=Scarlet & Violet (TCG)]] 166/198|G|{{TCG ID|Scarlet & Violet|Arven|166}}|Supporter||Uncommon|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbol